%% Patient OTP Authentication (WhatsApp)
sequenceDiagram
  actor P as Patient
  participant API as Next.js API
  participant DB as otp_requests / patients
  participant WA as Meta WhatsApp API
  P->>API: POST /api/otp/send (phone)
  API->>API: Generate 6-digit OTP, hash, 5-min expiry
  API->>DB: Store OTP request
  API->>WA: Send otp_authentication template
  WA-->>P: OTP delivered
  P->>API: POST /api/otp/verify (otp)
  API->>API: Check hash, expiry, attempts < 3
  alt Valid
    API->>DB: Find/create phone_account + patient
    API-->>P: JWT (role=patient) in httpOnly cookie
  else Invalid
    API-->>P: Reject (increment attempt)
  end
